Description
-----------

Prevents this material from casting shadows onto any surfaces.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

    noShadows

Parameters
----------

Not Available.

Notes
-----

This implies the [NoSelfShadow](NoSelfShadow_%28Material_global_keyword%29 "NoSelfShadow (Material global keyword)") global keyword.

